  "body": "## Proposal: Instrument the /api/v1 handlers \r\n**Use case. Why is this important?**\r\n~Currently, we have instrumentation for response codes on the `/api/v1/metrics` handler.~\r\nThe metrics endpoint at `/metrics` generates response code metrics. This is `promhttp_metric_handler_requests_total`.\r\n\r\nThe proposal is that we similarly instrument the handlers in `/api/v1/`, so that we can visualize and/or alert on these if we need to. \r\n\r\nEdit: Thanks @brian-brazil for the correction on `/metrics` not being in `/api/v1/`",
